&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;The Moloch Mentality&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Moloch the thoroughly unpleasant!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img src=&quot;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/this-page-intentionally-left-blank/Moloch.png&quot; alt=&quot;Moloch.png&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; /&gt;
